annotationA: Diphosphomevalonate decarboxylase; Performs the first committed step in the biosynthesis of isoprenes
annotationB: Quemao, isoform A; Geranyltranstransferase activity; dimethylallyltranstransferase activity; farnesyltranstransferase activity.
